---
alwaysApply: true
---

- After a relevant (non-trivial) change, always check the current version of the app in the README.md
  - check `docs/ChangeLog.md` and if the last changelog matches the same in the help tab, then bump the app version by `+0.001 (only in the changelog) and add a short changelog note for that new version.
  - if in `docs/ChangeLog.md` the version is higher that the one in HelpTab, then don't bump, just keep adding notes to the last version number.
  - al final del changelog pondrás entre [ ] una sugerencia de nombre corto para el commit que hará el usuario luego de este ajuste
  los changelogs siempre van en castellano!


